INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (6163, '<p>The Dative Pipeline API is provided by Deductive Inc of 145 Marina Boulevard, San Rafael, California, 94901 (Deductive, us or we).</p>\n\n<p>This licence agreement (Licence) covers the terms between your business (Licensee or you) and us for:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>The Deductive Data Pipeline at https://pipeline-api.deductive.com (Data Pipeline API)</li>\n	<li>Related online documents (Documentation).</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>By using the Data Pipeline API you agree to the terms of this licence. If you do not agree to the terms of this licence, you must not use the Data Pipeline API</p>\n\n<p>We licence use of the Data Pipeline API and Documentation to you on the basis of this Licence. We do not sell the Data Pipeline API or Documentation to you. We remain the owners of the Data Pipeline API and Documentation at all times.</p>\n\n<p><strong>1. Acknowledgements</strong></p>\n\n<p>1.1 The terms of this Licence apply to the Data Pipeline API or any of the services accessible through the Data Pipeline API (Services), including any updates or supplements to the Data Pipeline API or any Service, unless they come with separate terms, in which case those terms apply.</p>\n\n<p>1.2 We may change these terms at any time by sending you an email with details of the change. INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (7347, '<h1>Contact Us</h1>');
