INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (11829, '<h2>CUSTOM PANELS USING OTHER DATA OR DATA COMBINATIONS</h2>\n\n<p>Deductive can provide panel services for any matchable data set. We have extensive experience matching set top box data with Smart TV data and making the resulting combination representative.</p>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (11832, '<h2>PANEL SERVICE (NRP)</h2>\n\n<p>Some customers have licensed a granular data set and want to use that data set to measure behaviors of a national audience.</p>\n\n<p>To enable such measurement, Deductive offers a panel service in which we match the data set to one or more databases with specified demographics. We then use data science to produce weights for each household to balance the data set and make it as representative as possible</p>\n\n<p>We recently created a standard national panel for Inscape data. This includes the above service as well as a cull of TVs to only use those TVs best suited for measurement purposes.</p>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (11840, '<h1>Data generation Service</h1>\n\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\"> </div>\n</div>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (11842, '<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"195\">Many of our customers have existing raw datasets that they wish to leverage internally or with third parties. We have developed pipelines to collect, process, and normalize these datasets. This work typically includes a deep dive into the actual data available, its reliability and accuracy, followed by the development of a pipeline to process the data. We implement quarantine for wrong datasets and monitoring and alarms to be sure of data quality at all times.</p>\n\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"663\">With a clean dataset in place, we can then deliver data out to internal and external stakeholders and customers. They can then activate the data either in partnership with us or on their own.</p>\n\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"856\">Data Generation - Set Top Box ETL</p>\n\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"891\">Deductive previously developed a software stack for set top box generation. Deductive deployed and operated the solution on millions of set top boxes globally and generated real time granular set top box viewing data for multiple large operators for multiple years.</p>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (11848, '<h1>Data matching services</h1>\n\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\"> </div>\n</div>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (11850, '<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"224\">Most datasets have limited value in isolation but significant benefits when combined with other datasets. We have worked extensively with match partners such as LiveRamp, Experian, and 4info to connect our customers\' datasets and also develop technology for clients to directly match datasets to their in-house device graphs.</p>\n\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"551\">We measure the matching and validate the results of the match rate and the quality of the match. Do we see skews in the matched data that we need to take into consideration, and can we be sure that a match matches? Once we\'ve built confidence in the model, we document the processes and implement them into the clients\' data pipeline.</p>\n\n<h2>Clean Room Services for Data Matching</h2>\n\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"926\">Deductive can provide clean room services to enable privacy-safe matches, for example to assist marketers with use of their first party data for data driven TV applications such as planning, buying, measurement and optimization of ad campaigns.</p>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (11857, '<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"btn btn-info\" href=\"/latest/\">See the latest posts</a></div>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (11862, '<h1>Professional Services</h1>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (11864, '<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"188\">Deductive provides data centric professional services to clients ranging from data generators, including ACR and STB companies, to data platform providers, to end users of data such as networks, agencies and advertisers. In all cases, we help clients put data to work.</p>\n\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"457\">We work with many different types of data in a variety of vertical markets. Our primary data markets are Media and Automotive.</p>\n\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"585\">We build all sorts of models. We love models! And data science is really our core.</p>\n\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"669\">We also build infrastructure, dashboards, reporting services, pipelines, data lakes, anonymization systems, and publishing systems.</p>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (11911, '<h1>Data Science Consulting</h1>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (11913, '<p>Our data science team has core competencies in data normalization and fusion, identity matching, audience indexing, attribution and prediction. We have developed a set of processes based on our experience in handling huge TV, digital and media data sets.</p>\n\n<p>Our team has experience in machine learning and AI, unsupervised learning projects, generalized linear models and classification projects. We are AWS preferred partners, and carry out most of our projects on AWS. Our team is particularly skilled in using Python and SQL.</p>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (11919, '<h2 class=\"text-primary\">Data normalization</h2>\n\n<p>We have significant experience building normalized datasets from these Smart TV, set-top box and OTT datasets.</p>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (11924, '<h2 class=\"text-success\">Data matching</h2>\n\n<p>Our identity matching process achieves strong match rates across numerous TV and digital data sets, using deterministic and probabilistic matching.</p>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (11929, '<h2 class=\"text-info\">TV audience indexing</h2>\n\n<p>Our data monetization assessment process surfaces the most promising and lucrative opportunities, and provides customers with a clear path to execute on them.</p>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (11935, '<h2 class=\"text-primary\">Attribution</h2>\n\n<p>We have significant experience running attribution analyses, ranging from simple tune-in analysis to multi-touch attribution analysis across multiple campaigns and datasets.</p>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (11940, '<h2 class=\"text-success\">Subscriber analytics</h2>\n\n<p>Our data science team can build machine learning models that aid retention, upsell, subscriber acquisition and marketing effectiveness.</p>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (11945, '<h2 class=\"text-info\">Segmentation</h2>\n\n<p>Our data science team has built a segmentation approach that media companies can use to build customer segments for internal use or for targeting.</p>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (11952, '<h1>Data Engineering</h1>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (11954, '<p>Our team has deep experience in developing and optimizing the critical parts of a media company\'s data infrastructure, including onboarding, pipelines, warehousing and reporting.</p>\n\n<p>We have multiple development models. We can build one of these elements on a stand-alone basis or develop an end-to-end infrastructure incorporating several of these elements.</p>\n\n<p>Our team members are media specialists. Many of our engineers are Amazon Web Services-certified, and our team is also proficient with SQL on Hive, Presto and Redshift.</p>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (11960, '<h2 class=\"text-primary\">Data quality assessment</h2>\n\n<p>Poor quality data leads to bad decisions, and costs companies money. Media companies use our data quality tests to identify quality issues and get recommendations on fixing them.</p>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (11965, '<h2 class=\"text-success\">Data pipeline</h2>\n\n<p>The data pipeline is the most critical part of a company’s data architecture. Our pipeline process ensures there is consistency in your data, with minimum fuss.</p>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (11970, '<h2 class=\"text-info\">Dataset on-boarding</h2>\n\n<p>On-boarding a new dataset brings additional complexity to a data pipeline. We take all data through our standard on-boarding and cleansing process to ensure it flows reliably.</p>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (11976, '<h2 class=\"text-primary\">API development</h2>\n\n<p>A well-designed, flexible API makes it easy to ship data between parties. Our API development process is simple, consistent and designed with TV data in mind.</p>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (11981, '<h2 class=\"text-success\">Model productization</h2>\n\n<p>Taking a data science model from the sandbox to a production environment is fraught with pitfalls. Our processes help you scale your models with ease.</p>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (11986, '<h2 class=\"text-info\">Reporting automation</h2>\n\n<p>We will build and automate reports, in the business development tool of your choice, that run quickly and reliably, and get the right data points to the right people in your business.</p>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (11993, '<h1>Data Operations</h1>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (11995, '<p>Data operations is the art of getting data through to your data science teams in a timely, accurate, and efficient manner. Data feeds might arrive late, occasionally corrupted, and there are always new data suppliers to onboard. Data operations is the discipline that keeps the data flowing.</p><p>Our data operations team manages services that range from 100Mb a week to several hundred gigabytes a day. Data verification, systems management, and quality reporting come together to reduce the pain of data ingestions and allow your data science team to focus on data science, not data preparation.</p>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (12001, '<h2 class=\"text-primary\">Data infrastructure management</h2>\n\n<p>We can run and monitor an organization’s AWS infrastructure, including proactive identification of issues and optimizing reporting and usage with local teams.</p>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (12006, '<h2 class=\"text-success\">Reporting support</h2>\n\n<p>We can supply overflow resource to run ad-hoc requests and analysis; campaign analysis and optimization; tune-in reports, and more.</p>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (12011, '<h2 class=\"text-info\">Data cleansing</h2><p>We can operate data cleansing on an on-going basis with our Deductive Pipeline API.</p>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (12018, '<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"btn btn-info\" href=\"/latest/\">See the latest posts</a></div>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (12021, 'Latest updates from our Data Operations team');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (12061, '<h1>Data Partners</h1>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (12088, '<h1>COMBINING DATASETS</h1>\n\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\"> </div>\n</div>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (12094, '<p>Client problem/need: Customer had licensed both STB and smart TV datasets and wanted to combine the two together to have the best possible model.</p>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (12099, '<p>Deductive solution: We did a detailed comparison of the two datasets and built a model to create a single panel of national viewership based upon a combination of the two datasets. We tested and compared the results against industry benchmarks and implemented a daily production workflow.</p>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (12104, '<p>Outcome: Customer has switched measurement and reporting to the new panel and significantly increased revenues</p>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (12109, '<p>Time to market: 52 weeks</p>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (12117, '<p>US</p>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (12121, '<p>Set-top box, Smart TV, OTT</p>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (12125, '<p>National panel data, Multiple consumption data sets</p>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (12142, '<h1>Coffee with Tom and Michael</h1>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (12144, '<p>Coffee with Tom and Michael is a regular series of videos where Deductive\'s CEO Michael, in California, and CTO Tom, in England, discuss Deductive\'s work with TV datasets. In the first episode, they begin by drawing parallels between creating the perfect cup of coffee by blending various beans together and creating the perfect granular TV data by blending various datasets. Obtaining this granular TV data is not about starting with the ideal dataset; the trick is in the blending. Deductive is currently releasing its Best Practices white paper, which discusses the types of datasets typically used in TV data and the best practices for combining them.</p>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (12162, '<h1>About Us</h1>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (12164, '<p>Deductive is a Data Services company focusing on applications of granular TV data.</p>\n\n<p>We are data generalists, which means there are many things we do that apply to basically any data set, including strategy, data service design, data service implementation and management licensing, productization, transformation, cleaning, normalization and enrichment.</p>\n\n<p>We are also specialists in media applications and in particular TV data. We have extensive background and expertise in the generation, formation, licensing, productization, enrichment, combination and application of granular TV data.</p>\n\n<p>Within media markets, we have advanced developed solutions attribution, including data driven measurement of cross platform ad effectiveness, across linear TV advertising, addressable advertising CTV, OTT, and digital display advertising. We currently provide such attribution services to both buy side and sell side customers and have a very wide and deep data ecosystem to measure thousands of advertisers.</p>\n\n<p>We also provide data combining and data panel development and management services. The recently launched Nationally Representative Panel for Inscape Smart TV data enables Inscape licensees to produce more accurate measurement of ad and content viewership.</p>');
INSERT INTO `djangocms_text_ckeditor_text` VALUES (12185, '<h1>About Us</h1>');
