INSERT INTO `news_snippet_newssnippet` VALUES (8158, 'ViacomCBS says the covid-19 pandemic is an opportunity for broadcasters and advertisers to deepen their relationships', '2020-06-15 09:37:40.000000', 'https://www.beet.tv/2020/06/viacomcbss-ross-sees-pandemic-as-way-to-deepen-ties-with-advertisers.html', 8, '<p>ViacomCBS says that in spite of covid-19 and remote working, the company has been able to deepen its relationships with buyers since March, confirming the critical importance of personal relationships between ad buyers and sellers. ViacomCBS\'s chief advertising revenue officer also states that lockdown has enabled the coming together of two distinct business cultures from the recent merger of Viacom and CBS to happen more quickly and smoothly than is normally the case with such mergers.</p>');
INSERT INTO `news_snippet_newssnippet` VALUES (8159, 'NBCUniversal commits to helping small businesses recover from economic decline due to covid-19', '2020-06-15 12:04:19.000000', 'https://www.mediapost.com/publications/article/352513/nbcu-to-provide-marketing-creative-services-for-s.html', 8, '<p>NBCUniversal wants to help retailers open again as soon as possible and, as a result, will not charge content and commercial fees for small businesses. The iconic company has also set up an information hub that contains both financial and business content to offer advice to small businesses as they open up post-lockdown. It is also a part of the “Stand for Small” coalition, which helps SMEs to help connect entrepreneurs and customers.</p>');
INSERT INTO `news_snippet_newssnippet` VALUES (8160, 'CTV has now matured, making it ideal for advertisers to reach viewers they haven\'t reached elsewhere', '2020-06-15 12:32:59.000000', 'https://ppc.land/freewheel-connected-tv-is-now-a-mature-platform/', 8, '<p>According to Freewheel, CTV is following the same route which linear TV took in the past, meaning that it is becoming a replacement and not merely a supplement to traditional TV platforms. One similar pattern is how the consumption of ads rises during the day and then reaches a peak from 8-10 pm while viewers finish watching 97% of ads they start viewing.</p>');
INSERT INTO `news_snippet_newssnippet` VALUES (8161, 'Roku enables YouTube creators who specialize in shows for children and families to migrate to CTV', '2020-06-16 10:38:23.000000', 'https://www.adexchanger.com/tv-2/why-youtube-creators-are-flocking-to-ctv/', 8, '<p>The Roku Channel added a new section aimed specifically at kids and families at the end of last year, which included content from YouTube, giving YouTube creators an opportunity to expand their audiences and enter the streaming TV market. Pocket.watch, the CA-based entertainment company, attributes its 40% growth to its use of the Roku platform since 2019.</p>');
INSERT INTO `news_snippet_newssnippet` VALUES (8162, 'Disney and AMC Networks are the latest publishers to adopt addressability solutions', '2020-06-16 13:21:58.000000', 'https://www.fool.com/investing/2020/06/15/amc-disney-jumped-on-new-normal-tv-advertising.aspx', 8, '<p>Addressability is becoming more mainstream than ever, with first Disney and then AMC Networks making announcements during the last week. AMC stated it is joining an addressable television ad initiative started by three other cable firms while Disney is joining Nielsen\'s addressable TV beta program. This follows earlier moves towards embracing addressable by Comcast and CBS.</p>');
INSERT INTO `news_snippet_newssnippet` VALUES (8163, 'DTC brands adopting television to advertise during covid-19 are demanding digital quality measurement', '2020-06-22 14:16:24.000000', 'https://www.glossy.co/fashion/the-pandemic-is-making-tv-advertising-more-measurable-and-less-expensive-for-dtc-brands', 12, '<p>The best-performing DTC companies, who have traditionally tended to use digital to advertise their brands, are now doing so on TV as well, and are looking for the same kind of targeting and measurement results they are used to while advertising on digital platforms. The high cost of TV advertising amplifies their need for high-quality ROI metrics. OTT is in a better position to give these metrics than linear TV is. Traffic that a website receives through search is likely the best indicator of the success of a particular video ad.</p>');
INSERT INTO `news_snippet_newssnippet` VALUES (8164, 'Linear TV can use original content to reach a different audience from OTT', '2020-06-23 08:34:37.000000', 'https://www.beet.tv/2020/06/linear-tv-ott-can-complement-audience-reach-disneys-rita-ferro.html', 12, '<p>According to Disney, original content has a significant role to play in linear TV, which can complement the sports, news, and live events which have been its strength as it faces competition from OTT. Disney, which acquired content and legacy content-rich 21st Century Fox last year, said that original content drives both linear TV and OTT consumption.</p>');
INSERT INTO `news_snippet_newssnippet` VALUES (8165, 'Roku releases new ad tools to help buyers navigate uncertainty due to covid-19', '2020-06-23 12:03:09.000000', 'https://www.tubefilter.com/2020/06/22/roku-kicks-off-newfronts-ad-tools-pandemic/', 12, '<p>Roku, the CA-based digital media player manufacturer, has created its Agile Investment Plan tools to help advertisers and marketers, given the problems many businesses face in the wake of the pandemic. One of the aims is to help marketing teams with buying ads nationally while these tools also enhance purchasing safeguards, allow buyers to place ads solely on the top 1% of Roku\'s channelsm and avoid ad collisions from the same buyer.</p>');
INSERT INTO `news_snippet_newssnippet` VALUES (8166, 'Disney pitches Hulu to the biggest brands as OTT\'s most valuable partner', '2020-06-23 12:54:15.000000', 'https://deadline.com/2020/06/hulu-rolls-out-ad-buying-measurement-tools-disney-newfront-advertising-1202966097/', 12, '<p>Disney made the claim concerning Hulu, which it gained full control of in 2019, in a presentation to advertisers where it also unveiled new format and measurement tools for advertisers. The iconic company pointed out that OTT has matured into a must-have place for buyers while predicting that streaming TV\'s impact on advertising will be as significant as the impact search had 20 years ago.</p>');
INSERT INTO `news_snippet_newssnippet` VALUES (8167, 'Tubi set to allow advertisers to put a cap on ad spot frequency from any source', '2020-06-23 17:56:58.000000', 'https://variety.com/2020/digital/news/fox-tubi-lego-masters-ninjago-free-streaming-ad-frequency-caps-1234644365/', 12, '<p>Tubi, the SF-based ad-supported streaming service acquired by Fox in March, says that it is addressing a recurring complaint from both viewers and marketers by allowing advertisers to avoid double spotting with its new Advanced Frequency Management service. Both viewers and buyers have expressed frustration at the repetition of ads in OTT services, caused by aggregators accessing publishers\' inventory supplies.</p>');
